Name: Here I Come
About the game: One day you were kidnapped by a psycho named Freek, and forced into a secret underground facility to take part in a deadly reality show. The rules are simple: be the last one to survive. Meanwhile, thousands, if not millions, of people watch in real time and bid on who will win. 'Here I Come' is an atmospheric horror game in which learning when to hide or run are key factors to survive. Run for your life!
